<%- include("partials/header") %>

<main class="container">

<section class="hero-reviews">
  <img src="/images/hero-reviews.jpg" alt="Boxed Mac and Cheese Reviews">  
  <h1>Boxed Mac & Cheese Reviews</h1>
  <p>
    Not all boxed mac and cheese is created equal. We taste-test popular brands
    and rate them on flavor, creaminess, cheese quality, and nostalgia factor.
  </p>
</section>

<section class="reviews-grid">

  <div class="review-card">
    <img src="/images/kraft-mac.jpg" alt="Kraft Mac and Cheese">
    <h2>Kraft Mac & Cheese</h2>

    <div class="rating">
      Creaminess ⭐⭐⭐⭐☆
      <br>Flavor ⭐⭐⭐⭐☆
      <br>Cheese Powder ⭐⭐⭐⭐☆
      <br>Nostalgia ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐
    </div>

    <p>
      The classic boxed mac. Smooth, creamy, and iconic. The cheese powder
      dissolves perfectly and delivers the nostalgic flavor most people
      associate with mac and cheese.
    </p>
  </div>


  <div class="review-card">
    <img src="/images/annie-mac.jpg" alt="Annie's Mac and Cheese">
    <h2>Annie's Cheddar Mac</h2>

    <div class="rating">
      Creaminess ⭐⭐⭐☆☆
      <br>Flavor ⭐⭐⭐⭐☆
      <br>Cheese Powder ⭐⭐⭐☆☆
      <br>Nostalgia ⭐⭐⭐☆☆
    </div>

    <p>
      A more natural tasting mac with organic ingredients. The flavor is
      slightly sharper and less processed than classic boxed varieties.
    </p>
  </div>


  <div class="review-card">
    <img src="/images/velveeta-shells.jpg" alt="Velveeta Shells and Cheese">
    <h2>Velveeta Shells & Cheese</h2>

    <div class="rating">
      Creaminess ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐
      <br>Flavor ⭐⭐⭐⭐☆
      <br>Cheese Sauce ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐
      <br>Nostalgia ⭐⭐⭐⭐☆
    </div>

    <p>
      The creamiest boxed mac thanks to the liquid cheese packet.
      The shell pasta holds the sauce beautifully.
    </p>
  </div>


  <div class="review-card">
    <img src="/images/great-value-mac.jpg" alt="Great Value Mac and Cheese">
    <h2>Great Value Mac & Cheese</h2>

    <div class="rating">
      Creaminess ⭐⭐⭐☆☆
      <br>Flavor ⭐⭐☆☆☆
      <br>Cheese Powder ⭐⭐☆☆☆
      <br>Value ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐
    </div>

    <p>
      Budget-friendly mac that gets the job done. Not as rich or creamy
      as premium brands, but extremely affordable.
    </p>
  </div>

</section>

</main>

<%- include("partials/footer") %>